OBUIAPP_PARAMETER.NAME: Converted Amount
OBUIAPP_PARAMETER.DESCRIPTION: The monetary sum at which one unit of measure is changed to another.
OBUIAPP_PARAMETER.HELP: The Converted Amount is the result of multiplying the Source Amount by the Conversion Rate for this target currency.

OBUIAPP_PARAMETER.NAME: Order/Invoice
OBUIAPP_PARAMETER.DESCRIPTION: Orders and Invoices to be paid
OBUIAPP_PARAMETER.HELP: Orders and Invoices to be paid

OBUIAPP_PARAMETER.NAME: Payment
OBUIAPP_PARAMETER.DESCRIPTION: Payment event
OBUIAPP_PARAMETER.HELP: Payment event

OBUIAPP_PARAMETER.NAME: Deposit To
OBUIAPP_PARAMETER.DESCRIPTION: Financial Account to which the amount is going to be deposited.
OBUIAPP_PARAMETER.HELP: Financial Account to which the amount is going to be deposited.

OBUIAPP_PARAMETER.NAME: Amount on GL Items
OBUIAPP_PARAMETER.DESCRIPTION: Amount on GL Items
OBUIAPP_PARAMETER.HELP: Amount on GL Items

OBUIAPP_PARAMETER.NAME: Conversion Rate
OBUIAPP_PARAMETER.DESCRIPTION: The amount or quantity at which one unit of measure is changed to another.
OBUIAPP_PARAMETER.HELP: The Conversion Rate defines the rate (multiply or divide) to use when converting a source currency to an accounting currency.

OBUIAPP_PARAMETER.NAME: GL Item
OBUIAPP_PARAMETER.DESCRIPTION: G/L Items added as part of a given payment
OBUIAPP_PARAMETER.HELP: G/L Items added as part of a given payment

OBUIAPP_PARAMETER.NAME: Currency To
OBUIAPP_PARAMETER.DESCRIPTION: Target currency
OBUIAPP_PARAMETER.HELP: The Currency To defines the target currency for this conversion rate.

OBUIAPP_PARAMETER.NAME: Action Regarding Document
OBUIAPP_PARAMETER.DESCRIPTION: A drop down list box indicating the actions regarding document
OBUIAPP_PARAMETER.HELP: A drop down list box indicating the actions regarding document

OBUIAPP_PARAMETER.NAME: Document Type
OBUIAPP_PARAMETER.DESCRIPTION: A value defining what sequence and process setup are used to handle this document.
OBUIAPP_PARAMETER.HELP: The Document Type determines document sequence and processing rules

OBUIAPP_PARAMETER.NAME: Used Credit
OBUIAPP_PARAMETER.HELP: If the payment has some generated credit is the amount already used on other payments. If the payment does not have a generated credit amount is the amount of credit used on the payment.

OBUIAPP_PARAMETER.NAME: Sales Transaction
OBUIAPP_PARAMETER.DESCRIPTION: An indication that a transfer of goods and money between business partners is occurring.
OBUIAPP_PARAMETER.HELP: The Sales Transaction checkbox indicates if this item is a Sales Transaction.

OBUIAPP_PARAMETER.NAME: Expected Payment
OBUIAPP_PARAMETER.DESCRIPTION: Expected Payment
OBUIAPP_PARAMETER.HELP: Expected Payment

OBUIAPP_PARAMETER.NAME: Reference No.
OBUIAPP_PARAMETER.DESCRIPTION: The number for a specific reference.
OBUIAPP_PARAMETER.HELP: The reference number can be printed on orders and invoices to allow your business partner to faster identify your records.

OBUIAPP_PARAMETER.NAME: Payment Method
OBUIAPP_PARAMETER.DESCRIPTION: It is the method by which payment is expected to be made or received.

OBUIAPP_PARAMETER.NAME: Overpayment Action
OBUIAPP_PARAMETER.DESCRIPTION: A drop down list box indicating overpayment actions
OBUIAPP_PARAMETER.HELP: A drop down list box indicating overpayment actions

OBUIAPP_PARAMETER.NAME: Document Category
OBUIAPP_PARAMETER.DESCRIPTION: A classification of document types that are shown and processed in the same window.
OBUIAPP_PARAMETER.HELP: The Document Base Type identifies the base or starting point for a document. Multiple document types may share a single document base type.

OBUIAPP_PARAMETER.NAME: Organization
OBUIAPP_PARAMETER.DESCRIPTION: Organizational entity within client
OBUIAPP_PARAMETER.HELP: An organization is a unit of your client or legal entity - examples are store, department. You can share data between organizations.

OBUIAPP_PARAMETER.NAME: Standard Precision
OBUIAPP_PARAMETER.DESCRIPTION: Rule for rounding calculated amounts
OBUIAPP_PARAMETER.HELP: The Standard Precision defines the number of decimal places that amounts will be rounded to for accounting transactions and documents.

OBUIAPP_PARAMETER.NAME: Credit To Use
OBUIAPP_PARAMETER.DESCRIPTION: Credit to use in the current payment
OBUIAPP_PARAMETER.HELP: Credit to use in the current payment

OBUIAPP_PARAMETER.NAME: Actual Payment
OBUIAPP_PARAMETER.DESCRIPTION: Is the amount paid
OBUIAPP_PARAMETER.HELP: Is the amount paid

OBUIAPP_PARAMETER.NAME: Generate Credit
OBUIAPP_PARAMETER.DESCRIPTION: Amount left as credit on the payment.
OBUIAPP_PARAMETER.HELP: Amount left as credit on the payment.

OBUIAPP_PARAMETER.NAME: Order
OBUIAPP_PARAMETER.DESCRIPTION: A unique and often automatically generated identifier for a sales order.
OBUIAPP_PARAMETER.HELP: Unique identifier and a reference to a Sales Order originating from the document sequence defined for this document type.

OBUIAPP_PARAMETER.NAME: Total
OBUIAPP_PARAMETER.HELP: Total amount

OBUIAPP_PARAMETER.NAME: Payment Date
OBUIAPP_PARAMETER.DESCRIPTION: Date of the payment event. It is used in the posting record of the Payment to the general ledger. Defaulted to the Invoice Date field.
OBUIAPP_PARAMETER.HELP: Date of the payment event. It is used in the posting record of the Payment to the general ledger. Defaulted to the Invoice Date field.

OBUIAPP_PARAMETER.NAME: Amount on Invoices and/or Orders
OBUIAPP_PARAMETER.DESCRIPTION: Amount on Invoices and/or Orders
OBUIAPP_PARAMETER.HELP: Amount on Invoices and/or Orders

OBUIAPP_PARAMETER.NAME: Currency
OBUIAPP_PARAMETER.DESCRIPTION: An accepted medium of monetary exchange that may vary across countries.
OBUIAPP_PARAMETER.HELP: Indicates the currency to be used when processing this document.

OBUIAPP_PARAMETER.NAME: Received From
OBUIAPP_PARAMETER.DESCRIPTION: Is the Payee of the invoice. Defaulted to the Business Partner from the Invoice
OBUIAPP_PARAMETER.HELP: Is the Payee of the invoice. Defaulted to the Business Partner from the Invoice

OBUIAPP_PARAMETER.NAME: Payment Document No.
OBUIAPP_PARAMETER.DESCRIPTION: Document number of the payment
OBUIAPP_PARAMETER.HELP: Document number of the payment

OBUIAPP_PARAMETER.NAME: Transaction Type
OBUIAPP_PARAMETER.DESCRIPTION: Type of transaction
OBUIAPP_PARAMETER.HELP: The Transaction Type indicates the type of transaction to be submitted.

OBUIAPP_PARAMETER.NAME: Invoice
OBUIAPP_PARAMETER.DESCRIPTION: A document listing products, quantities and prices, payment terms, etc.
OBUIAPP_PARAMETER.HELP: The Invoice ID uniquely identifies an Invoice Document.
